{"tid":726597,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"曾將毒犯遊街示眾　菲律賓市長遭槍殺","createTime":"2018-07-02T14:00:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-02T14:29:31.000Z","uid":53379,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"3a23be8086b4b499cd4c15ce48baa54bfa1d0c63","tid":726597,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T14:00:42.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">曾將毒犯遊街示眾　菲律賓市長遭槍殺</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180702/s00005/876cc870d90d1ea8ee04bc27bc57426f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180702%2Fs00005%2F876cc870d90d1ea8ee04bc27bc57426f.jpg&h=09aee855&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖1之1 - 市長哈利利。(資料圖片)<br />\n<br />\n曾將毒犯遊街示眾的菲律賓八打雁省塔瑙安市（Tanauan）市長哈利利（Antonio Halili），今早在市政廳升旗儀式期間被槍殺，送院途中證實不治。<br />\n<br />\n當時市政府員工Gerry Yson Laresma在FB直播升旗儀式。片中哈利利和其他政府員工肅立唱國歌，突然一下槍聲響起，群眾尖叫四出逃跑。保安人員即場還火，導致群眾更加恐慌，希望快一點找到掩護。Laresma表示，哈利利因為強硬打擊罪案，曾經收到死亡威脅。<br />\n<br />\n在場副市長Jhoanna Corona-Villamor指出，當時看到哈利胸膛右側中槍，擔心他可能因此喪命，然後她開始逃走：「當我看到每個人都在避難時，我開始跑走。我進入市政廳後，仍然很害怕，然後我聽到更多的槍聲。我讓工作人員檢查是否有更多人受傷，感謝上帝沒有其他受害者。」<br />\n<br />\n有傳媒報道，現場迹象顯示，哈利利是遭狙擊手遠距離槍擊。<br />\n<br />\n哈利利2016年5月為響應總統當選人杜特爾特掃毒口號，在地方慶典上加插「毒販遊街」節目，下令11名販毒犯人貼有「我是毒販，不要學我」的紙卡，圍繞小鎮走一圈，當中有3人仍未成年。此舉遭到人權組織抨擊，更被封為「八打雁版杜特蒂」。<br />\n<br />\n哈利利亦在2017年10月，被杜特爾特列為涉毒地方首長名單，剝奪對地方警察的控制權；不過哈利利否認。<br />\n<br />\n(CNN/中央社)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180702/s00005/1530524256433\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180702%2Fs00005%2F1530524256433&d=RmGgjlo2L4VoqaZYwsVXVwKEmdudW1rq3V1Y15kzxIU%3D&h=72e3921e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180702%2Fs00005%2F1530524256433&h=dac7a984\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180702/s00005/1530524256433</a>"},{"pid":"38fe305361f836dd18db817f0a22c678fbd3f698","tid":726597,"uid":144372,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T14:03:22.000Z","msg":"如果香港通過咗國歌法<br />\n咁有人開槍要逃走算唔算唔莊重"},{"pid":"2a7211aa819aa08816555bc1dbe98ae09e41ef10","tid":726597,"uid":9098,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"38fe305361f836dd18db817f0a22c678fbd3f698","tid":726597,"uid":144372,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T14:03:22.000Z","msg":"如果香港通過咗國歌法<br />\n咁有人開槍要逃走算唔算唔莊重"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T14:07:59.000Z","msg":"點解咁都問得出口<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cd5f9525e63b3a6d52286dc0af5b61dde0422e3","tid":726597,"uid":32588,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T14:08:35.000Z","msg":"幾時到香城市長被槍殺"},{"pid":"b51b9d20fa31520cc3abca32f88a6e660ddded2d","tid":726597,"uid":116364,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T14:19:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"18875385a0fb3e02ef9166396d3ae629c337a8a3","tid":726597,"uid":116364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T14:20:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b20198d9c1419c8ae5bdd79936f791ac9f8ef479","tid":726597,"uid":116364,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T14:27:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c16f0d25082f086e06a1298a865907d8546bf1c8","tid":726597,"uid":63154,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T14:29:31.000Z","msg":"Shithole country自量下啦，學人打擊毒販，經濟咁差唔撈偏門食風咩，趕狗入窮巷咪同你死過囉，個總統小心啲呀，就快到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}